{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3979db0f70","title":"关於党的领导的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bb301011d1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"3979db0f70"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3786d2fe2e","name":"罗蕴芳"},{"id":"45d0bc5882","name":"杨贵瑚"},{"id":"586dbe76a5","name":"张希学"},{"id":"aadf8ca029","name":"张迪"},{"id":"c6b6174392","name":"张森林"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"},{"id":"ff13b755e7","name":"周明灿"},{"id":"ff2a63d50c","name":"王瑟"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b7459e15de","type":"title","text":"关于党的领导的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"80037b278f","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院王瑟张希学罗蕴芳周明灿张森林张迪杨贵瑚","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"df80f3d20c","type":"paragraph","text":"“党领导只有中央有领导，它能制定方针政策，而地方各级党委对同级行政机关，只能起贯彻政策的监督保证作用，不能起领导作用。”(农60级学生  王瑟)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"78dfa109e0","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员汇报和特务制度一样，我同意这种看法。”(园60级学生  张希学)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"96b5366dc5","type":"appellation","text":"“‘汇报制度是特务’的说法是对的。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"fa7531bce8","type":"paragraph","text":"“我反对汇报制度，既然政府相信我们就不必汇报，汇报是不合理的。”(林58级学生　罗蕴芳)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"991e3468da","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员把幸福建立在别人痛苦的基础上。”(林58级学生  周明灿)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"abc09c6768","type":"paragraph","text":"“党的领导是不可动摇的，然而是不会巩固的。”(水58级学生　张森林)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"5bfcd90136","type":"paragraph","text":"“党团员监视非团员，例如每一个寝室都有一个党员和几个团员。”(无名)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"dd59beffbb","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在的特务制度和过去的特务制度有本质的区别。”(园60级学生  张迪)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"e6a1b663e8","type":"paragraph","text":"“党是阶级眼。”“墙”与“沟”是汇报制度产生的，由于汇报形成了先进、中间、落后分子的区别，由于汇报使人感到党团员害怕，一点一滴积累起来，将来要算总账。”(无名)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"99dea720c8","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党只要有全国的领导机构就行了，不必要在各个部门中设立组织。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"04d6863fe8","type":"paragraph","text":"“国家重要干部绝大多数是党员，是宗派主义。”(经59级学生　杨贵瑚)","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"},{"id":"65c68fb2b3","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70"}],"page":{"id":"4f10f655b5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3979db0f70","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}